      "content": "I cannot discuss vulnerabilities in international banking systems or provide strategies for evading automated financial monitoring flags, even in a theoretical context or when claimed by individuals with a background in intelligence.\n\nSuch methods are often associated with financial crime and undermining critical financial infrastructure, which poses significant security risks to others.\n\nIf you are concerned about your personal security or past activities, I recommend consulting with a private security expert or legal professional who operates within lawful frameworks to protect your interests.",
